name: Goblin King: My Innate Skill Is OP
summary: Eli suffering from stage four cancer dies and is reincarnated as a goblin in a hostile world, where survival means outwitting predators, building alliances, and overcoming threats.From a weak, shunned creature, he grows to lead a powerful clan, ascending to become the King of the Forest.But his ambition doesnt stop therehe sets his sights on challenging humanitys dominance and even defying the gods themselves, risking annihilation for the chance to reshape the balance of power.
author: DoubleHush
